raw_data.title: Graphic Designer 1
raw_data.description: Performs a variety of full life-cycle application design functions for existing and new software systems.  Assists in interface design.  Generate wireframes, logos, and functional components to be developed by software engineers.  Works closely with software engineers to ensure feasibility of design and ensure it is developed to specification.  Evaluates method for access, visualizing, and interacting with information in an intuitive way.  Evaluates final software application to assist in identification of design flaws and opportunities for improvement.  Works under the direction of a Senior Graphics Designer or technical lead.
